name: md-to-pptx
description: >
  Reads a markdown report file and generates a professional executive
  PowerPoint presentation using pptxgenjs. Designed for weekly retail
  AI intelligence reports.
input_schema:
  type: object
  properties:
    md_path:
      type: string
      description: Full path to the source .md file
    output_path:
      type: string
      description: Full path where the .pptx should be saved
    theme:
      type: string
      description: Color theme - "dark" (navy/blue) or "light" (white/blue)
      default: dark
  required:
    - md_path
    - output_path
implementation: |-
  1. Read the markdown file at md_path
  2. Parse sections: Core Overview, Enterprise Updates, Case Analysis,
     IKEA Recommendations, Risks
  3. Run: npm install -g pptxgenjs (if not installed)
  4. Generate a Node.js pptxgenjs script with:
     - Slide 1: Cover (title, date, classification)
     - Slide 2: Weekly Core Overview
     - Slide 3-N: One slide per enterprise update
     - Slide N+1: Case Analysis (3 cases)
     - Slide N+2: IKEA Recommendations
     - Slide N+3: Risks & Observations
  5. Save to output_path
  6. Confirm file exists and return the output path
